npc/sinta: The portal ahead leads to Stage 4 — the gambling platform itself. The inside of the machine.
npc/sinta: Everything you've seen was just the delivery system. The ads, the spam, the phishing, the debt enforcement — all of it existed to funnel people and their money through that portal.
npc/sinta: I've been to the edge of it. It looks like a casino. Bright lights. No windows. No clocks. Nothing inside reminds you that time — or your bank balance — still exists outside.
npc/sinta: But the gate is locked. The key waits at the top of this climb — find it, and Stage 4 opens. Watch for the glowing line; it will point the way.
npc/sinta: Past the portal it stops being about money and starts being about the mind. Guard yourself.
npc/sinta: One more thing. In the real world, if you or someone you know is drowning in gambling debt — you are not alone, and it is not hopeless.
npc/sinta: Call 119 extension 8. They will not judge you. They will help.
npc/sinta: Now go. Find the key. You are almost there.
